Install:
  sudo install pluzz /usr/local/bin

Play video:
  pluzz play http://www.pluzz.fr/jt-20h.html

Record video:
  pluzz record http://www.pluzz.fr/jt-20h.html

Get stream URL:
  pluzz url http://www.pluzz.fr/jt-20h.html

Author and infos (in French):
  http://blog.rom1v.com/2010/07/pluzz-fr-france-televisions-lance-son-service-de-tv-de-rattrapage-non-lisible/
